[b]Installation:[/b] Just download with Nexus mod manger, Mod organizer or manual,if you want to install it manually,then you have to extract it into your data                       file for Skyrim.

[b]Unistallation:[/b]  Just untick in mod manger or mod organzier or delete the files you manually installed.
